works.description:
An image with the a quote by author Earl 

Grollman it states:

"Grief is not a disorder, a disease or sign of weakness. It is an  
emotional, physical and spiritual necessity, the price you pay for love.  

The only cure for grief is to grieve" and has been done graphically  
appealing.

The bottom of the image has our logo and url for our not for profit
website  
unspokengrief.com, which has been cropped out by the infringing url.
